<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.1">
<l>porumā nīḷpaṭai yāḻicaṅ kattoṭu</l>
<l>tirumā nīḷkaḻa lēḻula kuntoḻa</l>
<l>vorumā ṇikkuṟa ḷāki nimirntavak</l>
<l>karumā ṇikkameṉ kaṇṇuḷa tākumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the fighting big long weapon, the discus, the conch,</l>
<l>while the seven worlds worship [his] sacred big long anklet[ted feet],</l>
<l>that black ruby who strechted out after having become</l>
<l>a dwarf is what is in my eyes.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
